  <Summary>Step into a world where the shadows of the past forge the heroes--and monsters--of tomorrow. Jason Bronze is a man on the edge, driven by a thirst for vengeance against the sinister Doctor Acid, the serial killer who robbed him of his parents. But as the echoes of World War II fade, a new peril arises from the depths of mad science, threatening to alter the fabric of reality.

In an electrifying twist on the classic Frankenstein mythos, witness the birth of a hero unlike any other—a beacon of hope in a world teetering on the brink of darkness. This groundbreaking comic book saga ushers in a dazzling Golden Age universe where gods walk among us and monsters lurk in every shadow.

Prepare for an adventure that transcends life and death itself. “Harrowing #1”—where every page crackles with the raw energy of a bygone era, reimagined for a new generation of gods and monsters. Don’t miss the epic beginning of a legend—grab your copy today!</Summary>
